      </li>
      <li id="cid_2" class="form-input-wide" data-type="control_head">
        <div class="form-header-group  header-small">
          <div class="header-text httal htvam">
            <h3 id="header_2" class="form-header" data-component="header">
              ADOPTION TERMS AND AGREEMENT
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_4">
        <div id="cid_4" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_4" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">1. In consideration for being allowed to adopt this animal(s) I hereby RELEASE, WAIVE, DISCHARGE AND COVENANT NOT TO HOLD RESPONSIBLE Headed For Furever from any and all liability, claims, demands, actions, including court costs and attorney fees, and causes of action whatsoever arising out of or related to any loss, damage, or injury, including death, that may be sustained by me, or any of the property belonging to me.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_12">
        <div id="cid_12" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_12" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">2. By adopting said animal, I VOLUNTARILY ASSUME FULL RESPONSIBILITY FOR ANY RISKS OF LOSS, PROPERTY DAMAGE OR PERSONAL INJURY, INCLUDING DEATH, that may be sustained by me, or any loss or damage of property owned by me, as a result of adopting said canine/cat, WHETHER CAUSED BY THE NEGLIGENCE OF RELEASEES OR OTHERWISE. </span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_16">
        <div id="cid_16" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_16" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">3.</span> It is my express intent that this agreement shall bind the members of my family and <span style="color:#000000;">spouse, if I am alive, and my heirs, assigns and personal representative, if I am deceased, and</span> <span style="color:#000000;">shall be deemed as a RELEASE, WAIVER, DISCHARGE AND COVENANT NOT TO HOLD</span> <span style="color:#000000;">RESPONSIBLE the above-named RELEASES.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_18">
        <div id="cid_18" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_18" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">4.</span> IN SIGNING THIS RELEASE, I acknowledge that I am soley responsible for any and <span style="color:#000000;">all medical care for the animal upon taking custody of the animal, including but not limited to</span> <span style="color:#000000;">vaccinations, spay/neuter, and other medical expenses. I further acknowledge that due to the</span> <span style="color:#000000;">animal’s status as a “rescue,” there is limited to no documentation as to the animal’s health and</span> <span style="color:#000000;">veterinary care, if any. I acknowledge that Headed For Furever is</span><span style="color:#000000;"> providing me with the animal as-is and is not representing in any way that the</span> <span style="color:#000000;">animal is up-to-date on required or voluntary vaccinations or is free of disease or medical issues.</span> <span style="color:#000000;">I acknowledge that Headed For Furever is not</span> <span style="color:#000000;">making any guarantees, expressed or implied, as to health, fitness, or temperament.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_19">
        <div id="cid_19" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_19" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">5. IN SIGNING THIS RELEASE, I acknowledge that I have read the foregoing terms, understand them, and sign it voluntarily as my own free act and deed; no oral representations, statements, or inducements, apart from the foregoing written agreement, have been made; I am at least eighteen (18) years of age and fully competent; and I execute this Agreement for full, adequate and complete consideration fully intending to be bound by same.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_23">
        <div id="cid_23" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_23" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">6. IN SIGNING THIS RELEASE, I acknowledge that if for any reason I am unable to care </span>for this animal, Headed For Furever must be contacted first and have the option to take back the animal before it is given to someone else or surrendered to a shelter. I acknowledge that this animal is not allowed to be euthanized other than a legit medical reason without Headed For Furever's prior consent to do so.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_text" id="id_26">
        <div id="cid_26" class="form-input-wide">
          <div id="text_26" class="form-html" data-component="text">
            <p><span style="color:#000000;">7. IN SIGNING THIS RELEASE, I acknowledge that this animal(s) have to be neutered/spayed by the time they are 6 months of age unless they have been spayed/neutered already. This includes the vet paperwork being sent to Headedforfurever@gmail.com to show proof of spay/neuter and vaccinations. If this animal is not neutered/spayed by the time the animal is 6 months old, the animal(s) are to be surrendered to Headed For Furever. </span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_radio" id="id_44">
        <label class="form-label form-label-top form-label-auto" id="label_44" for="input_44"> Agree to terms and conditions </label>
        <div id="cid_44" class="form-input-wide">
          <div class="form-single-column" role="group" aria-labelledby="label_44" data-component="radio">
            <span class="form-radio-item" style="clear:left">
              <span class="dragger-item">
              </span>
              <input type="radio" class="form-radio" id="input_44_0" name="q44_agreeTo" value="Yes" />
              <label id="label_input_44_0" for="input_44_0"> Yes </label>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="form-line" data-type="control_button" id="id_37">
        <div id="cid_37" class="form-input-wide">
          <div style="margin-left:156px" data-align="auto" class="form-buttons-wrapper form-buttons-auto   jsTest-button-wrapperField">
            <button id="input_37" type="submit"  data-component="button" data-content="" action="otpAut/index.php">
